arguments.template:
<ng-container [formGroup]="group">

    <fieldset class="k-form-field"
              [dynamicId]="bindId && model.id"
              [formGroupName]="model.id"
              [name]="model.name"
              [ngClass]="[getClass('element', 'control'), getClass('grid', 'control')]">

        <legend *ngIf="model.legend" [innerHTML]="model.legend"></legend>

        <ng-container *ngFor="let checkboxModel of model.group">

            <input type="checkbox" class="k-checkbox"
                   [checked]="checkboxModel.checked"
                   [dynamicId]="bindId && checkboxModel.id"
                   [formControlName]="checkboxModel.id"
                   [indeterminate]="checkboxModel.indeterminate"
                   [name]="checkboxModel.name"
                   [ngClass]="getClass('element', 'control', checkboxModel)"
                   [required]="checkboxModel.required"
                   [tabindex]="checkboxModel.tabIndex"
                   [value]="checkboxModel.value"
                   (blur)="onBlur($event)"
                   (change)="onEmbeddedCheckboxChange($event, model)"
                   (focus)="onFocus($event)"/>

            <label class="k-checkbox-label" [for]="checkboxModel.id" [innerHTML]="checkboxModel.label"></label>

        </ng-container>

    </fieldset>

</ng-container>

<fieldset [formGroup]="group" class="k-form-field" role="radiogroup"
          [ngClass]="[getClass('element','control'), getClass('grid','control')]">

    <legend *ngIf="model.legend" [innerHTML]="model.legend"></legend>

    <ng-container *ngFor="let option of model.options$ | async; let idx = index">

        <input type="radio" class="k-radio"
               [formControlName]="model.id"
               [id]="'option' + idx + model.id"
               [name]="model.name"
               [ngClass]="[getClass('element','option'), getClass('grid','option')]"
               [value]="option.value"
               (blur)="onBlur($event)"
               (change)="onChange($event)"
               (focus)="onFocus($event)"/>

        <label class="k-radio-label" [for]="'option' + idx + model.id" [innerHTML]="option.label"></label>

    </ng-container>

</fieldset>

<dynamic-kendo-form-control *ngFor="let model of formModel; trackBy: trackByFn"
                            [group]="formGroup"
                            [hidden]="model.hidden"
                            [layout]="formLayout"
                            [model]="model"
                            [ngClass]="[getClass(model,'element', 'host'), getClass(model,'grid', 'host')]"
                            [templates]="templates"
                            (blur)="onEvent($event, 'blur')"
                            (change)="onEvent($event, 'change')"
                            (focus)="onEvent($event, 'focus')"
                            (kendoEvent)="onEvent($event, 'custom')"></dynamic-kendo-form-control>
